Are you having trouble having a decent conversation with your kids? Well, here's some inspiration. JOHANNESBURG - A video of a father chatting with his 18-month-old son has taken over the internet. The video of the adorable conversation was initially posted by the mother Shanieke Pryor on Facebook and so far it has been viewed more than 35 million times and shared more than 1.1 million times on social media. Several celebrities including Captain America Chris Evans shared the video with his followers with the caption: “I could’ve watched an hour of this.”